 Home Ancestors Family Lines Elizabeth Leathers Berry Gen 1 Robert Berry × Mary Williamson — Princess Anne County, Virginia Gen 2 Robert Berry × Elizabeth Cate — Orange County, North Carolina Gen 3David J. Berry × Mary Blalock — Orange County, North Carolina Generation 3 (stepdaughter) Elizabeth Leathers Berry Born c. 1791 Died Unknown Married Unknown Parents Mary Blalock and William Riley (biological father); adopted by David J. Berry Sr. Explore in the Berry Family Timeline Elizabeth Leathers Berry, Was The Daughter Of Mary Blalock# Elizabeth Berry was born before David J. Berry married Mary Blalock. She is not blood related to the Berry family but David J. Berry adopted his step daughter and she was raised with his own children. As far as I know there is no knowledge of who she married or what kind of life she was able to make for herself after David J. Berry and her mother, Mary Blalock, died. Elizabeth was the illegitimate daughter of William Riley, who was brought to court about the matter. A bastardy bond was placed on him. This is the same William Riley against whom Elizabeth Berry (daughter of Robert and Elizabeth Cate Berry) also filed a bastardy bond in August 1791. Elizabeth was born about 1791 Children of Elizabeth Leathers Berry To be Researched
